# Documentation — Limerence Workspace

## Source of truth

**`docs/` in Limerence-Workspace** — единственный canonical source. Notion — для обсуждений.

## Layers

| Layer | Path | Use for |
|-------|------|---------|
| **Domain** | `docs/monetization/` | SKU, catalog, entitlements, billing |
| **Spec** | `docs/specs/` | Gameplay entities, paywall BR, analytics, policies |
| **Impl** | `docs/monetization/*_PLAN.md`, `docs/web/` | Code maps, constructor architecture |
| **Meta** | `docs/_meta/` | Conventions, glossary, discrepancy matrix |

## Scope tags

Declare at task start: `mobile` | `web` | `shared` | `cross-cutting`

| Scope | Primary paths |
|-------|---------------|
| mobile | `mobile/src/**` |
| web | `web/editor-app/**` |
| shared | `docs/monetization/`, `supabase/`, `docs/specs/gameplay/entities/` |
| cross-cutting | monetization, analytics schema, chapter release |

## Code references

Use workspace-relative `@see`:

```ts
/** @see docs/specs/gameplay/entities/Глава.md */
/** @see docs/specs/monetization/paywall.md */
/** @see docs/monetization/ENTITLEMENTS.md */
```

Never use legacy `Спецификация/` paths.

## Workflow

1. Read canonical doc before gameplay/monetization changes
2. Update doc + code in same task
3. Cross-cutting: check `docs/_meta/discrepancy-matrix.md`
4. Run `scripts/validate-docs.sh` after doc edits

## Key index

| Need | Read first |
|------|------------|
| Gameplay entity | `docs/specs/gameplay/entities/` |
| Paywall UI | `docs/specs/monetization/paywall.md` |
| SKU / entitlements | `docs/monetization/PRODUCT_MODEL.md`, `ENTITLEMENTS.md` |
| Constructor | `docs/web/codebase-overview.md` |
| Path migration | `docs/_meta/path-mapping.md` |
